{"tid":455074,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"努力過好每一日咁又點？最想分享同佢個個永遠都唔會返黎架啦","createTime":"2017-11-01T18:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T05:01:07.000Z","uid":127417,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"635430f40c59dd4b8c952f90974fdf35d9f13d79","tid":455074,"uid":127417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:23:03.000Z","msg":"係呀 好弱智<br />\n人本來就應該為左自己生活<br />\n唔應該比其他影響自己情緒<br />\n<br />\n成日以為自己放得底 不斷話比自己聽唔再掛住佢<br />\n因為人地都唔掛住你啦<br />\n點都好 你幾掛住佢都好,唔可以比佢知你冇左佢唔得<br />\nYes my ego is big<br />\n<br />\n但其實我仲好掛住你,就算有其他人既出現<br />\n都改變唔到你係我心入面個位<br />\n<br />\n好想再聽你把聲,好想再電話震個時見到係你打比我<br />\n好想每日見到任何開心事都同你分享<br />\n<br />\n可惜你既最愛唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd1baf179424e13c603d39984b3edec1d014891","tid":455074,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"move on"},{"pid":"5a7894902dad4d03e5c97f4174cdfda0876ddeb3","tid":455074,"uid":127417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"點解我要掛住一個完全唔掛住我既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb5761376d5758c37a92b0091bd04d770149630","tid":455074,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dPmZqsQNzGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdPmZqsQNzGA&d=5vWcKq%2FNKKtnvWSXd8ZgDgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f9924a81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dPmZqsQNzGA</a>"},{"pid":"fd4d6a527adc270247818547205172c9cf8e470a","tid":455074,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀 好弱智<br />\n人本來就應該為左自己生活<br />\n唔應該比其他影響自己情緒<br />\n<br />\n成日以為自己放得底 不斷話比自己聽唔再掛住佢<br />\n因為人地都唔掛住你啦<br />\n點都好 你幾掛住佢都好,唔可以比佢知你冇左佢唔得<br />\nYes my ego is big<br />\n<br />\n但其實我仲好掛住你,就算有其他人既出現<br />\n都改變唔到你係我心入面個位<br />\n<br />\n好想再聽你把聲,好想再電話震個時見到係你打比我<br />\n好想每日見到任何開心事都同你分享<br />\n<br />\n可惜你既最愛唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要時間去move on<br />\n始終習慣咗佢 唔容易放下的<br />\n起碼你知人生係為自己而活 得自己先會陪自己一世 有痛有難題都要自己去面對 其他人只係輔助嘅角色<br />\n<br />\n人生好短暫的 係難放下的 但你可以好快放得低的 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會有更適合你的係前面<br />\nit takes time to move on but plz don't lose your confidence and your smile<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29499bde680a2aef1f3afbc2070667e23364c581","tid":455074,"uid":12324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T19:45:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f288e7d54f624be06cb2f57e89c2c518b1a93081","tid":455074,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要move on<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當一個人成為你嘅過客 佢仲係你嘅心佔有好重嘅位置 令你唔開心嘅 move on會好d<br />\n<br />\n不過其實呢d嘢逼唔嚟 越想move on就越放唔低 好似係"},{"pid":"45b8f8594e3ae31c3aa2d4d6b7532d1f22bb892d","tid":455074,"uid":154816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"完全係我心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54915c3e6e9fb324853424f4fa1aa47ca520c8b","tid":455074,"uid":19065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"我都明白種感受, 分手係女方提出就係一句唔夠愛, 所以選擇唔要我<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得曾經講過要努力工作賺錢去令佢第時會做我嘅老婆仔, 就算屋都會係買係佢屋企附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後又如何? 一句無feel 所有野完哂<br />\n<br />\n我只係同自己講我值得一個會會珍惜我嘅人<br />\n<br />\n叫自己move on, 但係琴晚5點又係諗起佢醒咗"},{"pid":"64251a03a6587f57053786b73bc4c6db3c83fffe","tid":455074,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci